OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FMost of the UK's biggest businesses
OL,8,Fhave hit targets for gender
OL,9,Frepresentation in their boardroom, but
OL,10,Ffall short when it comes to women
OL,11,Fleaders who face greater scrutiny and
OL,12,Funconscious bias, according to
OL,13,FGovernment-backed report.
OL,15,FData from the FTSE Women Leaders
OL,16,FReview shows that women held 43% of
OL,17,Fboard positions on FTSE 350 companies
OL,18,Fin 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
