PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FIt marks a significant leap towards
OL,8,Fgender balance in the boardrooms of
OL,9,Fthe UK's biggest listed companies,
OL,10,Ffrom the 9.5% recorded when the review
OL,11,Fbegan 15 years ago.
OL,13,FNevertheless, the proportion is more
OL,14,For less the same than it was in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FVivienne Artz, chief executive of the
OL,8,FFTSE Women Leaders Review, said the
OL,9,F"pace of change is naturally beginning
OL,10,Fto level as parity approaches",
OL,11,Fadding: "Boards are still making
OL,12,Fprogress, which is great, but there's
OL,13,Fnot as much progress to make."
OL,15,FThe review, which is supported by the
OL,16,FGovernment, tracks the progress of the
OL,17,FFTSE 350 and 50 of the UK's largest
OL,18,Fprivate companies towards voluntary
OL,19,Fgender representation targets.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@^O]sD@IOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe latest report revealed that the
OL,8,Fproportion of women in leadership
OL,9,Fpositions on the FTSE 350 has edged up
OL,10,Fto 36%, from 35% the previous year, as
OL,11,Fof the end of October 2025.
OL,13,FWithin that, the proportion of women
OL,14,Fin chief executive roles was 8%, up
OL,15,Ffrom 7%.
OL,17,FThere were nine women chief executives
OL,18,Fat FTSE 100 companies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThere has been a recent flurry of
OL,8,Ffemale bosses quitting from top listed
OL,9,Fcompanies and being replaced by men,
OL,10,Fsuch as Dame Emma Walmsley from drug
OL,11,Ffirm GSK, Liv Garfield from water
OL,12,Fsupplier Severn Trent, and Diageo's
OL,13,FDebra Crew.
OL,15,FOn the other hand, energy giant BP
OL,16,Fappointed its first ever female chief
OL,17,Fexecutive, who is due to step into the
OL,18,Frole in April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FMs Artz said firms were making slow
OL,8,Fprogress when it comes to gender
OL,9,Fbalance for the CEO, chair and finance
OL,10,Fdirector roles.
OL,12,F"It's because they are incredibly
OL,13,Fdemanding and difficult roles to
OL,14,Ffill," she told the Press Association.
OL,16,F"I think that too often we rely on the
OL,17,Fsafe option which is, 'we're going to
OL,18,Fhave have someone who's done it
OL,19,Fbefore'.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@FO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"And if you're always going back to
OL,8,Ffishing in the same pond then you're
OL,9,Fnot finding new talent... you're not
OL,10,Flooking at skills and expertise, as
OL,11,Fopposed to a CV that you feel
OL,12,Fcomfortable with and you're seen
OL,13,Fbefore," she said.
OL,15,FFurthermore, Ms Artz said women can
OL,16,Fface barriers to leadership positions
OL,17,Fdue to prevailing attitudes which have
OL,18,F"not been easy to dismantle".
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]zD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"I think we can say that female CEOs
OL,8,Fget a lot more scrutiny and they get
OL,9,Fjudged on different things that male
OL,10,FCEOs do," she said.
OL,12,FShe said that talking points such as
OL,13,Fwhether the person is married or has
OL,14,Fchildren can be "distracting, and in
OL,15,Fmany ways it diminishes the
OL,16,Fcredibility of the leader".
OL,18,F"We do know that there is absolutely
OL,19,Fstill unconscious bias and that
OL,20,Fthere's attitudes that need to
OL,21,Fchange," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@IO]vD@QOUxD@ZO]zD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FMs Artz also argued that the cost of
OL,8,Fchildcare means that families are led
OL,9,Fto making decisions that can "derail"
OL,10,For "sideline" a woman's career.
OL,12,FResponding to the report, Chancellor
OL,13,FRachel Reeves said the data "shows how
OL,14,Ffar we've come", adding: "But there is
OL,15,Fstill a long way to go as women remain
OL,16,Funderrepresented in key executive
OL,17,Froles.
OL,19,F"As Chancellor, I'm clear there should
OL,20,Fbe no ceiling on a woman's ambition.
OL,26,@qD@^OUqD@eO]rD@DOUrD@MO]uD@]OUvD@OO]vD@
OL,26,AZOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"When they can participate fully at
OL,8,Fevery level, organisations make better
OL,9,Fdecisions, innovate more and perform
OL,10,Fmore strongly, boosting our whole
OL,11,Feconomy."
OL,13,FBusiness and Trade Secretary Peter
OL,14,FKyle said: "It's essential that our
OL,15,Ftop talent can reach the highest
OL,16,Flevels of leadership, which is why I'm
OL,17,Fso pleased the UK continues to lead
OL,18,Fthe charge for gender equality in
OL,19,Fboardrooms.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]vD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"However, be in no doubt that despite
OL,8,Fthis progress, there is still much
OL,9,Fmore work to do."
OL,11,FLooking at individual companies,
OL,12,Fdrinks giant Diageo and supermarket
OL,13,Fand services chain The Co-operative
OL,14,FGroup have the highest representation
OL,15,Fof women in their boardrooms, at 77.8%
OL,16,Fand 72.7% respectively.
OL,18,FMarks & Spencer, HSBC, and water firms
OL,19,FSevern Trent and Pennon Group are
OL,20,Famong those to record representation
OL,21,Fgreater than 60%.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771909410
OL,3,CWomen bosses face more scrutiny than
OL,4,Cmen, says chief of Government-backed
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FAt the other end of the scale, parcel
OL,8,Fgiant Evri and yoghurt maker Muller
OL,9,Fhad no women on their boards, while
OL,10,Fthe likes of pub groups Mitchells &
OL,11,FButlers and Wetherspoons were towards
OL,12,Fthe bottom of the list with
OL,13,Frepresentation of 22%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
